{"pageProps":{"entry":{"id":"local-what-comes-after-july","title":"What Comes After July","date":"2026-07-05","slug":"what-comes-after-july","categories":["Learning","Work"],"mood":"Reflective","summary":"July 4 I fly back to Taiwan. July 5 I sit the JLPT N2 exam. After that? I honestly don't know yet. Here's what I'm thinking.","wordCount":472,"location":"Singapore","source":"local","mdxSources":{"en":{"compiledSource":"var m=Object.defineProperty,d=Object.defineProperties;var u=Object.getOwnPropertyDescriptors;var o=Object.getOwnPropertySymbols;var s=Object.prototype.hasOwnProperty,r=Object.prototype.propertyIsEnumerable;var h=(e,t,a)=>t in e?m(e,t,{enumerable:!0,configurable:!0,writable:!0,value:a}):e[t]=a,i=(e,t)=>{for(var a in t||(t={}))s.call(t,a)&&h(e,a,t[a]);if(o)for(var a of o(t))r.call(t,a)&&h(e,a,t[a]);return e},l=(e,t)=>d(e,u(t));var p=(e,t)=>{var a={};for(var n in e)s.call(e,n)&&t.indexOf(n)<0&&(a[n]=e[n]);if(e!=null&&o)for(var n of o(e))t.indexOf(n)<0&&r.call(e,n)&&(a[n]=e[n]);return a};const layoutProps={},MDXLayout=\"wrapper\";function MDXContent(a){var n=a,{components:e}=n,t=p(n,[\"components\"]);return mdx(MDXLayout,l(i(i({},layoutProps),t),{components:e,mdxType:\"MDXLayout\"}),mdx(\"h1\",null,\"What Comes After July\"),mdx(\"p\",null,\"There's something clarifying about having two hard deadlines in the same week.\"),mdx(\"p\",null,`July 4: flight to Taipei.\nJuly 5: JLPT N2 exam.`),mdx(\"p\",null,\"After that, the calendar is blank. Not empty in a bad way \\u2014 blank in the way a whiteboard is blank before a planning session. Full of possibility and slightly terrifying.\"),mdx(\"h2\",null,\"What I know for certain\"),mdx(\"p\",null,\"I'm going back to Taiwan. That part isn't uncertain. It's where my family is, where my roots are, where I want to spend some time before deciding what the next chapter looks like.\"),mdx(\"p\",null,\"Singapore has been a chapter, not a destination. That was always the frame. When I moved here, I told myself: \",mdx(\"em\",{parentName:\"p\"},\"build something, learn the region, figure out what comes next.\"),\" I've done the first two. The third is the one that requires July to pass.\"),mdx(\"h2\",null,\"What I think I know\"),mdx(\"p\",null,\"SkyReal continues regardless of geography. The company doesn't live in a city \\u2014 it lives in the product and the team. Post-July, I'll probably be running it from Taipei for a while, which will mean a different timezone for some calls but not a fundamental change to how we work.\"),mdx(\"p\",null,'JLPT N2 \\u2014 assuming I pass \\u2014 opens Japan as a real option. Not immediately, not necessarily. But the language barrier being reduced from \"significant obstacle\" to \"manageable friction\" changes the calculus on a lot of things.'),mdx(\"p\",null,\"The next wave of infrastructure I'm interested in building is at the intersection of AI and distributed teams. The region \\u2014 Southeast Asia, Taiwan, Japan \\u2014 is where a lot of this is actually being deployed. Being here rather than reading about it from California still seems like the right call.\"),mdx(\"h2\",null,\"What I don't know\"),mdx(\"p\",null,\"I don't know if I'll stay in Asia or head back to the Valley. The honest answer is that it depends on what SkyReal needs, and I don't know what SkyReal will need in September.\"),mdx(\"p\",null,\"I don't know if the JLPT studying has been enough. Probably. Probably not enough. July 5 will tell me.\"),mdx(\"p\",null,\"I don't know what I'll miss about Singapore. Probably more than I expect. It always works that way with places.\"),mdx(\"h2\",null,\"The frame I'm using\"),mdx(\"p\",null,\"I've been thinking of the last several years as a series of experiments rather than a career path. Each one had a question: \",mdx(\"em\",{parentName:\"p\"},\"Can I build something people want?\"),\" \",mdx(\"em\",{parentName:\"p\"},\"Can I operate across cultures?\"),\" \",mdx(\"em\",{parentName:\"p\"},\"Can I learn a new language as an adult?\")),mdx(\"p\",null,\"The experiments don't end in July. They just recalibrate.\"),mdx(\"p\",null,\"The 96 days are the sprint before the sprint. The real question \\u2014 what kind of person do I want to be in the next phase \\u2014 is the one I'm still working on.\"),mdx(\"p\",null,\"I'll have some answers by July 5. Then I'll start on the next set of questions.\"))}MDXContent.isMDXComponent=!0;\n","scope":{}},"zh":{"compiledSource":"var u=Object.defineProperty,D=Object.defineProperties;var L=Object.getOwnPropertyDescriptors;var o=Object.getOwnPropertySymbols;var m=Object.prototype.hasOwnProperty,r=Object.prototype.propertyIsEnumerable;var h=(p,e,t)=>e in p?u(p,e,{enumerable:!0,configurable:!0,writable:!0,value:t}):p[e]=t,a=(p,e)=>{for(var t in e||(e={}))m.call(e,t)&&h(p,t,e[t]);if(o)for(var t of o(e))r.call(e,t)&&h(p,t,e[t]);return p},y=(p,e)=>D(p,L(e));var s=(p,e)=>{var t={};for(var n in p)m.call(p,n)&&e.indexOf(n)<0&&(t[n]=p[n]);if(p!=null&&o)for(var n of o(p))e.indexOf(n)<0&&r.call(p,n)&&(t[n]=p[n]);return t};const layoutProps={},MDXLayout=\"wrapper\";function MDXContent(t){var n=t,{components:p}=n,e=s(n,[\"components\"]);return mdx(MDXLayout,y(a(a({},layoutProps),e),{components:p,mdxType:\"MDXLayout\"}),mdx(\"h1\",null,\"\\u4E03\\u6708\\u4E4B\\u5F8C\"),mdx(\"p\",null,\"\\u540C\\u4E00\\u9031\\u5167\\u6709\\u5169\\u500B\\u786C\\u622A\\u6B62\\u65E5\\u671F\\uFF0C\\u9019\\u4EF6\\u4E8B\\u6709\\u4E00\\u7A2E\\u8B93\\u4EBA\\u6E05\\u9192\\u7684\\u529B\\u91CF\\u3002\"),mdx(\"p\",null,`\\u4E03\\u6708\\u56DB\\u65E5\\uFF1A\\u98DB\\u5F80\\u53F0\\u5317\\u7684\\u73ED\\u6A5F\\u3002\n\\u4E03\\u6708\\u4E94\\u65E5\\uFF1AJLPT N2\\u8003\\u8A66\\u3002`),mdx(\"p\",null,\"\\u90A3\\u4E4B\\u5F8C\\uFF0C\\u884C\\u4E8B\\u66C6\\u662F\\u7A7A\\u767D\\u7684\\u3002\\u4E0D\\u662F\\u90A3\\u7A2E\\u4E0D\\u597D\\u7684\\u7A7A\\u767D\\u2014\\u2014\\u800C\\u662F\\u8A08\\u756B\\u6703\\u8B70\\u958B\\u59CB\\u4E4B\\u524D\\u767D\\u677F\\u7684\\u90A3\\u7A2E\\u7A7A\\u767D\\u3002\\u5145\\u6EFF\\u53EF\\u80FD\\